---
const { variant = "default" } = Astro.props;
---
<section class={variant === "inline" ? "" : "section"} style={variant === "inline" ? "" : "padding-top:0"}>
  <h2 class="h2">Why it works</h2>
  <p class="lead">
    Students learn faster when they can build, test, and explain. The kit makes invisible steps visible, so concepts move from notes to memory.
  </p>
  <ul class="muted" style="margin:.4rem 0 0">
    <li>• Color coding and shape cues guide correct pairing</li>
    <li>• Directional pieces show strand polarity</li>
    <li>• Codon grouping maps directly to a translation chart</li>
    <li>• Quick resets support multiple classes a day</li>
  </ul>
</section>

